nts and here to stay similarly our fund managers all invest in majedie funds further aligning our interests with those of our clients we view our capacity as scarce we believe investment performance suffers from diseconomies of scale if assets under management grow too large we are determined to maintain the size advantage for our clients and therefore limit the available capacity in each of our funds assets under management total approximately £bn bn     previous pause next news  jan  majedie uk income fund passes fifth anniversary milestone read more news  oct  majedie named a greenwich quality leader in uk institutional asset management read more news  oct  james de uphaugh and chris field recognised for a decade of investing excellence read more uk equity fund  majedie asset management skip to main content majedie asset management contact us search form search this site client login uk equity fund disclaimer you must read the following information in full and then choose an option at the foot of this text ‘agree’ will allow you to continue using this site subject to the disclaimer or ‘disagree’ which will limit the areas of the site you are able to view full terms of use can be found here the contents of this site have been prepared solely for information purposes majedie asset management limited does not provide financial investment tax or any other professional advice in any way and none of the information on this site should be construed as such none of the information contained on this site constitutes an offer to buy or sell or a solicitation by or on behalf of majedie asset management limited to buy or sell any security product service or investment any opinions expressed on this site do not constitute investment advice and independent advice should be sought where appropriate majedie asset management limited is authorised and regulated by the financial conduct authority under the financial services and markets act  of the united kingdom this site is direc